<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 04 Feb 2024 16:07:08 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>以色列的犹太阿拉伯学校如何应对加沙战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-02-04/ty-article-opinion/.premium/how-a-jewish-arab-school-in-israel-copes-with-war-in-gaza/0000018d-7372-d971-a38f-73f29a680000</link><description>犹太人和巴勒斯坦人正在经历以不同方式席卷我们的可怕暴力，而彼此之间却极度缺乏同情心。但在我女儿的学校，一些家庭失去了居住在加沙的亲人，另一些家庭则在 10 月 7 日失去了亲人，每天早上孩子们和老师都会出现，致力于弄清楚如何共同生活</description><pubDate>Sun, 04 Feb 2024 15:44:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-02-04/ty-article-opinion/.premium/how-a-jewish-arab-school-in-israel-copes-with-war-in-gaza/0000018d-7372-d971-a38f-73f29a680000</guid></item><item><title>以色列反政府抗议运动领导人希克玛·布雷斯勒回应将她与哈马斯联系起来的阴谋论</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-04/ty-article/israeli-protest-movement-leader-responds-to-conspiratorial-claims-linking-her-to-hamas/0000018d-7489-dd6e-a98d-f4ab7d5c0000</link><description>希克马·布雷斯勒是反对内塔尼亚胡政府司法改革的以色列抗议运动的代表人物之一，他被利库德集团议员指控与哈马斯有联系并参与了 10 月 7 日的袭击，他说，“毒药机器永远不会停止工作”。</description><pubDate>Sun, 04 Feb 2024 15:18:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-04/ty-article/israeli-protest-movement-leader-responds-to-conspiratorial-claims-linking-her-to-hamas/0000018d-7489-dd6e-a98d-f4ab7d5c0000</guid></item><item><title>当麦迪逊广场花园挥舞纳粹党徽旗帜时：“一切都可以归咎于犹太人”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-02-04/ty-article-magazine/.premium/when-swastika-flags-were-waved-on-madison-square-garden/0000018d-64c4-d915-ad8d-f5fcf4df0000</link><description>一部新纪录片以一个从 1936 年到 1941 年欺骗了 10 万美国人的纳粹组织为主题，该纪录片的创作者将当年的犹太人仇恨与今天的反犹太主义进行了比较</description><pubDate>Sun, 04 Feb 2024 14:04:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-02-04/ty-article-magazine/.premium/when-swastika-flags-were-waved-on-madison-square-garden/0000018d-64c4-d915-ad8d-f5fcf4df0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列科技产业乌云密布</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/business/2024-02-04/ty-article-magazine/.premium/dark-clouds-gather-for-israels-tech-industry/0000018d-5fc1-d7f9-a3af-dfe939060000</link><description>加沙战争导致科技行业领导者出现悲观情绪：越来越多的证据表明，以色列科技行业正在落后于世界其他地区，就业预测黯淡、投资下降以及报告大规模招聘的公司数量下降</description><pubDate>Sun, 04 Feb 2024 13:34:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/business/2024-02-04/ty-article-magazine/.premium/dark-clouds-gather-for-israels-tech-industry/0000018d-5fc1-d7f9-a3af-dfe939060000</guid></item><item><title>两名以色列人因涉嫌向耶路撒冷基督教修道院院长吐口水而被捕</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-04/ty-article/.premium/two-israelis-arrested-on-suspicion-of-spitting-on-a-christian-abbot-in-jerusalem/0000018d-73de-d971-a38f-73fef8f50000</link><description>犹太人在耶路撒冷老城向基督徒礼拜者或附近吐口水的事件已变得普遍，引起了以色列政府官员和宗教领袖的谴责，但一些知名人士认为向基督徒吐口水是“古老的犹太习俗”</description><pubDate>Sun, 04 Feb 2024 12:22:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-04/ty-article/.premium/two-israelis-arrested-on-suspicion-of-spitting-on-a-christian-abbot-in-jerusalem/0000018d-73de-d971-a38f-73fef8f50000</guid></item><item><title>“特拉维夫正在地下室举办派对”：以色列顶级厨师适应新现实</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-04/ty-article-magazine/.premium/tel-aviv-is-currently-partying-in-basements-top-israeli-chefs-adjust-to-a-new-reality/0000018d-6517-d7f7-adcf-6ddf4f040000</link><description>著名的米其林指南不会来，游客也不会来。哈马斯 10 月 7 日大屠杀之后，以色列美食界如何生存？正如一位成功的厨师所说：“F* 米其林”</description><pubDate>Sun, 04 Feb 2024 10:43:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-04/ty-article-magazine/.premium/tel-aviv-is-currently-partying-in-basements-top-israeli-chefs-adjust-to-a-new-reality/0000018d-6517-d7f7-adcf-6ddf4f040000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军预备役军人在加沙地带战斗行动中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-04/ty-article/idf-reservist-killed-in-gaza-strip-combat-operations/0000018d-7337-dd6e-a98d-f737edd20000</link><description>以色列军方宣布，一名24岁士兵周六在加沙南部被杀</description><pubDate>Sun, 04 Feb 2024 09:33:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-04/ty-article/idf-reservist-killed-in-gaza-strip-combat-operations/0000018d-7337-dd6e-a98d-f737edd20000</guid></item><item><title>以色列在帆板世界锦标赛上获得金牌和铜牌</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-04/ty-article/.premium/israel-comes-home-with-gold-and-bronze-medals-at-windsurfing-world-championships/0000018d-732a-dd6e-a98d-f72ae6250000</link><description>在加那利群岛举行的 2024 年帆板世界锦标赛上，两名以色列女子获得奖牌，莎朗·坎特 (Sharon Kantor) 获得金牌，队友凯蒂·斯皮恰科夫 (Katy Spychakov) 获得铜牌。坎特有望代表以色列参加今年夏天的巴黎奥运会</description><pubDate>Sun, 04 Feb 2024 09:12:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-04/ty-article/.premium/israel-comes-home-with-gold-and-bronze-medals-at-windsurfing-world-championships/0000018d-732a-dd6e-a98d-f72ae6250000</guid></item><item><title>极右翼部长本-格维尔在《华尔街日报》采访中表示，“如果特朗普掌权”，美国对加沙的看法将会有所不同</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-04/ty-article/far-right-minister-ben-gvir-says-in-wsj-interview/0000018d-72ea-d971-a38f-73fa99c30000</link><description>国家安全部长本-格维尔攻击拜登政府，谈到在经济上激励巴勒斯坦人离开加沙，并重申他反对任何释放巴勒斯坦囚犯的人质协议</description><pubDate>Sun, 04 Feb 2024 07:20:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-04/ty-article/far-right-minister-ben-gvir-says-in-wsj-interview/0000018d-72ea-d971-a38f-73fa99c30000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队承认未经授权进行图形影响加沙行动</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-02-04/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-its-admits-staff-was-behind-graphic-gaza-telegram-channel/0000018d-70b4-dd6e-a98d-f4b6a9c00000</link><description>以色列国防军的一个心理战部队在未经批准的情况下开设了一个针对以色列受众的 Telegram 频道。军方最初否认参与其中，但《国土报》曝光后的内部调查显示其参与其中</description><pubDate>Sun, 04 Feb 2024 06:57:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-02-04/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-its-admits-staff-was-behind-graphic-gaza-telegram-channel/0000018d-70b4-dd6e-a98d-f4b6a9c00000</guid></item><item><title>欧盟考虑是否根据美国行政命令对“极端主义”以色列定居者实施制裁</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-04/ty-article/.premium/eu-mulls-whether-to-impose-sanctions-on-extremist-israeli-settlers/0000018d-71cc-dd6e-a98d-f5eed2050000</link><description>欧盟需要一致投票支持对暴力的约旦河西岸定居者实施制裁，拜登采取行动后这一决定已“加快”</description><pubDate>Sun, 04 Feb 2024 06:02:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-04/ty-article/.premium/eu-mulls-whether-to-impose-sanctions-on-extremist-israeli-settlers/0000018d-71cc-dd6e-a98d-f5eed2050000</guid></item><item><title>拜登向内塔尼亚胡提供生命线，但以色列总理仍拒绝接受</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-04/ty-article/.premium/biden-offered-netanyahu-a-lifeline-but-the-prime-minister-still-refuses-to-take-it/0000018d-70b3-d4f1-a18d-f4f3e2070000</link><description>白宫已开始在中东引入“拜登主义”，尽管内塔尼亚胡仍然使以色列的地位变得脆弱。与此同时，美国一直在小心避免与伊朗发生全面军事对抗</description><pubDate>Sun, 04 Feb 2024 05:59:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-04/ty-article/.premium/biden-offered-netanyahu-a-lifeline-but-the-prime-minister-still-refuses-to-take-it/0000018d-70b3-d4f1-a18d-f4f3e2070000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军称有 15 枚火箭弹袭击以色列北部；哈马斯预计周日对人质交易做出回应</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-04/ty-article-live/u-s-and-allies-strike-over-30-houthi-targets-in-yemen-to-re-stabilize-red-sea/0000018d-7217-d4f1-a18d-f6776d6a0000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡：之前人质协议的比例将作为即将达成的协议的参考点 ■ 民意调查：29％的人赞成美国总统乔·拜登对以色列与哈马斯战争的处理方式 ■ 沙特消息人士称，哈马斯将于周日晚间对拟议的人质协议作出回应 ■ 以色列政府未批准向加沙扣押的人质发放工资，以色列国防军宣布中士死亡。西蒙·耶霍舒亚·阿苏林 (Shimon Yehoshua Asulin) 少校，24 岁，在加沙战斗中身亡 ■ 美军袭击胡塞武装反舰导弹 ■ 以色列军队袭击黎巴嫩真主党目标</description><pubDate>Sun, 04 Feb 2024 04:02:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-04/ty-article-live/u-s-and-allies-strike-over-30-houthi-targets-in-yemen-to-re-stabilize-red-sea/0000018d-7217-d4f1-a18d-f6776d6a0000</guid></item><item><title>数千名以色列人在特拉维夫集会，要求达成协议释放人质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-04/ty-article/.premium/thousands-of-israelis-rally-in-tel-aviv-to-demand-a-deal-to-release-the-hostages/0000018d-7113-dd6e-a98d-f5337bdc0000</link><description>人质家属呼吁战时内阁“续签公民与国家之间的契约”，数千名以色列人支持，纪念 10 月 7 日以来的 120 天</description><pubDate>Sun, 04 Feb 2024 00:36:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-04/ty-article/.premium/thousands-of-israelis-rally-in-tel-aviv-to-demand-a-deal-to-release-the-hostages/0000018d-7113-dd6e-a98d-f5337bdc0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列希望立即释放人质；如果不完全停火，哈马斯不会让步</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-04/ty-article/.premium/israel-wants-hostages-freed-all-at-once-hamas-wont-budge-without-complete-cease-fire/0000018d-70c9-d971-a38f-71fbbfc50000</link><description>熟悉以色列和哈马斯谈判的消息人士称，两国距离达成协议还有很长的路要走，但双方都不反对达成一项协议。</description><pubDate>Sat, 03 Feb 2024 22:48:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-04/ty-article/.premium/israel-wants-hostages-freed-all-at-once-hamas-wont-budge-without-complete-cease-fire/0000018d-70c9-d971-a38f-71fbbfc50000</guid></item><item><title>报告称，以色列军方对近东救济工程处指控的泄露感到惊讶</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-03/ty-article/israeli-military-surprised-by-leak-of-unwra-accusations-report-says/0000018d-7089-d971-a38f-71bb73470000</link><description>《纽约时报》调查显示，1月18日，联合国驻加沙机构总干事会见了一名以色列外交官，该外交官透露了该机构员工参与袭击事​​件，并在一周内将该信息发送给联合国和美国</description><pubDate>Sat, 03 Feb 2024 20:46:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-03/ty-article/israeli-military-surprised-by-leak-of-unwra-accusations-report-says/0000018d-7089-d971-a38f-71bb73470000</guid></item><item><title>“你应对 10 月 7 日大屠杀负责”：以色列各地数千人抗议内塔尼亚胡政府</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-03/ty-article/.premium/you-are-responsible-for-the-oct-7-holocaust-thousands-protest-against-netanyahus-govt/0000018d-705a-d971-a38f-71fa927b0000</link><description>耶路撒冷的一名退休以色列国防军将军表示，本届政府未能就人质返回问题做出决定，未能就结束战争的政治愿景做出决定，也未能就 20 万难民返回家园做出决定。</description><pubDate>Sat, 03 Feb 2024 20:31:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-03/ty-article/.premium/you-are-responsible-for-the-oct-7-holocaust-thousands-protest-against-netanyahus-govt/0000018d-705a-d971-a38f-71fa927b0000</guid></item><item><title>数百人在哥伦比亚大学外抗议，谴责以色列是“新纳粹德国”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-02-03/ty-article/.premium/denouncing-israel-as-the-new-nazi-germany-hundreds-protest-outside-columbia-university/0000018d-7091-dd6e-a98d-f4b3eca80000</link><description>反以色列抗议者高喊“起义万岁”和“定居者，定居者回家——巴勒斯坦是我们的”，沿着百老汇蔓延了几个街区，有时涌入街道并阻塞交通</description><pubDate>Sat, 03 Feb 2024 20:15:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-02-03/ty-article/.premium/denouncing-israel-as-the-new-nazi-germany-hundreds-protest-outside-columbia-university/0000018d-7091-dd6e-a98d-f4b3eca80000</guid></item><item><title>众议院共和党将推动向以色列提供超过 170 亿美元紧急援助的独立法案</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-02-03/ty-article/.premium/republicans-to-push-bill-providing-israel-with-17-6-billion-in-emergency-funding/0000018d-7084-dd6e-a98d-f4a6347e0000</link><description>该法案将于下周提出，正值参议院民主党人和共和党人就边境安全妥协问题进行紧张谈判，该妥协将为拜登的国家安全补充法案扫清道路，其中包括向以色列提供超过 140 亿美元的援助</description><pubDate>Sat, 03 Feb 2024 20:02:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-02-03/ty-article/.premium/republicans-to-push-bill-providing-israel-with-17-6-billion-in-emergency-funding/0000018d-7084-dd6e-a98d-f4a6347e0000</guid></item><item><title>加沙人报告哈马斯在以色列军队撤离的加沙北部地区恢复文官治理</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-03/ty-article/gazans-report-resurgence-of-hamas-civilian-governance-north-gaza-vacated-by-idf/0000018d-6fc6-d4f1-a18d-fff640bb0000</link><description>哈马斯在加沙最大城市卷土重来的迹象突显了该组织的韧性，尽管自 10 月 7 日对以色列发动致命袭击引发战争以来的四个月里，以色列发动了致命的空中和地面行动</description><pubDate>Sat, 03 Feb 2024 17:48:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-03/ty-article/gazans-report-resurgence-of-hamas-civilian-governance-north-gaza-vacated-by-idf/0000018d-6fc6-d4f1-a18d-fff640bb0000</guid></item></channel></rss>